<p>Argentière is 9km from Chamonix. The <i>Petit Balcon Nord</i> is a woodland walk between the two and has a picturesque playground. There&rsquo;s a river beach for paddling in. An unusual thing about this playground is that is impossible to drive to which makes a change.</p>
